    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏的主要焦点是其无声叙事，这意味着故事是在没有文字或对话的情况下讲述的。通过使用人物表情、音乐和视觉语言的场景来展开活跃的情节。探索、战斗和头目战都在简短的叙事场景之间进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，游戏教程和菜单也不使用任何文字。因此，除了游戏的标题/徽标之外，游戏中不存在任何语言，即使不懂英语也可以享受游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事概要</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当暴风雨袭来时，一名妇女渴望失去她失去的丈夫。然后奇怪的人物袭击了她。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/973f0c1c48a61a4d7959f43bc18c8f36.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/48d4fe726e68a923d213173ce2432ebb.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/4289d013f155699cac2a115fef804f72.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的士兵进来迫使她逃进树林里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/ac632b76ba72fa4e098e43f019bd4272.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/ac2dd44d8140d0cbc9fb43ba41eabd68.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/73cda3a72ddd495184cd9c164df819f2.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那里，她遇到了一个她似乎认识的陌生人，尽管他不认识她。两人继续躲避风暴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/d9653a49453335d5016ec81f89c0a282.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/9607bed2e5849c505717954543cfc741.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/4bf9c8874dcd0191df33aba9810fd3cf.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来到邻近城市寻求庇护时，一个意想不到的人在那里等着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/1e2edd136af717a8a89cdeaa62bf1a95.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正确地安排格挡时间来招架敌人的攻击并降低他们的耐力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/24a402c79e38f1811f20d5527fb27767.poster.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/24a402c79e38f1811f20d5527fb27767.webm?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/24a402c79e38f1811f20d5527fb27767.mp4?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当敌人的体力耗尽时，他们会陷入短暂的眩晕状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/74956ed0144361e2ca3c63202f9f7a30.poster.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/74956ed0144361e2ca3c63202f9f7a30.webm?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/74956ed0144361e2ca3c63202f9f7a30.mp4?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过躲避来避免无法阻挡的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/60d7871e728f576c9311aba5596ed76a.poster.avif?t=1761276833\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/60d7871e728f576c9311aba5596ed76a.webm?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284910/extras/60d7871e728f576c9311aba5596ed76a.mp4?t=1761276833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人并探索将积累经验值并提升玩家角色的等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏的预计游戏时间应在 3 小时左右。</p>",
